    <headline>Snow, yellow level, Outer areas of Hordaland and northern Rogaland, 2022-12-08T03:00:00+00:00, 2022-12-09T06:00:00+00:00</headline>
    <description>From early Thursday morning, the first snow fall of the year is expected. Until Friday morning upwards of 5 cm of snow is expected. There is large uncertainty in the forecast. Some places will not get snow.</description>
    <instruction>Allow some extra time for transportation and driving. Use tires fit for winter conditions and use caution while driving. The need for emergency preparedness shall be assessed continuously by emergency response actors. </instruction>
